data.description: LOVELY HOME IN A FANTASTIC LOCATION!! Split Foyer home featuring a ''MANCAVE'' downstairs with functioning WET BAR, SPACIOUS DEN AREA WITH working wood burning fireplace, and a SPRAWLING, LEVEL BACK YARD. Home is located on a nice CORNER LOT right down the road from Pleasant Ridge Elementary school and zoned for Karns High. This 3br 2.5 ba home has all 3 bedrooms on the main level and 2 full baths. Seller has not got to spend much time here since they purchased in 2021, they are having to relocate for military purposes. Pics to come 2/9/2024 and SHOWINGS BEGIN 2/12/2024.
